thread.title: Strange happening

author: news24.com
title: Strange happening
text:
We have a citizens group via an app on our smart phones in Klerksdorp. Yesterday at about 3 pm a strange occurrence took place. It was reported over a wide area from Potchefstroom to all around Klerksdorp.
It is difficult to describe but was almost like a plane going through the sound barrier or even an earthquake. But I heard no noise note did I feel any movement. Almost as if a huge object was moving past and compressed the air.
